1:23:40.000Z","msg":"Face ID 資料並不會離開您的裝置，也絕不會備份至 iCloud 或任何其他地方。只有在您想提供 Face ID 診斷資料給 AppleCare 來尋求支援時，此資訊才會從您的裝置傳輸出去。而即使在這種情況下，資料也不會自動傳送給 Apple；在傳送診斷資料之前，您可以先檢查並核准資料送出。<br />\n<br />\n若要使用 Face ID，您必須先在 iPhone 上設定密碼。在下列情況下，您必須輸入密碼以進行額外的安全驗證：<br />\n裝置剛開機或重新啟動。<br />\n裝置超過 48 小時未曾解鎖。<br />\n過去六天半內未使用密碼來解鎖裝置，且過去 4 小時內未以 Face ID 解鎖。<br />\n裝置收到遠端鎖定命令。<br />\n比對面孔失敗五次之後。<br />\n同時按住任一音量按鈕與側邊按鈕 2 秒鐘來啟動關機/SOS 緊急服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT208108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT208108&d=ZMIILXoNzp4iQkVGFJjd%2B8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=22511861\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT208108</a>"},{"pid":"f3fedf09fd1346e7971617ba47dd76992cece664","tid":431340,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:27:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">溫馨提示</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港電訊商目前除咗數碼通（SMT）係獨家用緊愛立信（瑞典通訊設備供應商）作電話網絡訊號接收之外，其他電訊一律都係用華為設備（有中國解放軍背景的中國通訊設備供應商）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"7b22147d29f2a578db974f498783810192529d3a","tid":431340,"uid":55951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">溫馨提示</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港電訊商目前除咗數碼通（SMT）係獨家用緊愛立信（瑞典通訊設備供應商）作電話網絡訊號接收之外，其他電訊一律都係用華為設備（有中國解放軍背景的中國通訊設備供應商）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n所以就可以自願俾人姦？"},{"pid":"735bac3cba19928f8df7da0006f2507b753409be","tid":431340,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">溫馨提示</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港電訊商目前除咗數碼通（SMT）係獨家用緊愛立信（瑞典通訊設備供應商）作電話網絡訊號接收之外，其他電訊一律都係用華為設備（有中國解放軍背景的中國通訊設備供應商）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n所以就可以自願俾人姦？</blockquote><br />\n咪話咗faceid資料唔會經apple server<br />\n咁你仲想點啫<br />\n加密擺喺電話到都唔俾<br />\n最好直接用念力解鎖好冇"},{"pid":"7a85f7b227a57f507314f517eade3e46d2cb43c7","tid":431340,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Face ID 資料並不會離開您的裝置，也絕不會備份至 iCloud 或任何其他地方。只有在您想提供 Face ID 診斷資料給 AppleCare 來尋求支援時，此資訊才會從您的裝置傳輸出去。而即使在這種情況下，資料也不會自動傳送給 Apple；在傳送診斷資料之前，您可以先檢查並核准資料送出。<br />\n<br />\n若要使用 Face ID，您必須先在 iPhone 上設定密碼。在下列情況下，您必須輸入密碼以進行額外的安全驗證：<br />\n裝置剛開機或重新啟動。<br />\n裝置超過 48 小時未曾解鎖。<br />\n過去六天半內未使用密碼來解鎖裝置，且過去 4 小時內未以 Face ID 解鎖。<br />\n裝置收到遠端鎖定命令。<br />\n比對面孔失敗五次之後。<br />\n同時按住任一音量按鈕與側邊按鈕 2 秒鐘來啟動關機/SOS 緊急服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT208108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT208108&d=ZMIILXoNzp4iQkVGFJjd%2B8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=22511861\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT208108</a></blockquote><br />\nan dog is blind"},{"pid":"af8b1dcf19b8d64d0fe2cb4c5838518fef68baeb","tid":431340,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:53:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://images.apple.com/business/resources/docs/FaceID_Security_Guide.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.apple.com%2Fbusiness%2Fresources%2Fdocs%2FFaceID_Security_Guide.pdf&d=ZMIILXoNzp4iQkVGFJjd%2B8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=e661ec7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://images.apple.com/business/resources/docs/FaceID_Security_Guide.pdf</a><br />\nApple有出white paper講faceid<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58bce6633cf62758a269a938cb33b3c8819fbb5","tid":431340,"uid":134717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor